sourcesContent: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { DashboardService } from "../dashboard.service"; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { UserbackService } from 'src/app/services/userback.service'; @Component({ selector: 'top-bar', templateUrl: './top-bar.component.html', }) export class TopBarComponent { isDropdownOpen = false; sidebarOpen: boolean = true; // Initially open constructor(private dashboard: DashboardService, private router: Router, private userbackService: UserbackService) {} openSidebar() { this.dashboard.openSidebar(); } toggleDropdown() { this.isDropdownOpen = !this.isDropdownOpen; } logout() { this.userbackService.logout().subscribe( (response: any) => { // Specify the type of response console.log('Logout successful', response); // Clear the token from localStorage localStorage.removeItem('authToken'); // Navigate to the login page after successful logout this.router.navigate(['/admin/login']); }, (error: any) => { // Specify the type of error console.error('Logout failed', error); // Handle logout error here } ); } editP(){ this.router.navigate(['/admin/editP']); } }
